</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Three friends sit on a bench overlooking the Togetsukyo bridge, on a sunny spring day. 晴れた春の日のこと、3人の友人が渡月橋を見下ろすベンチに座っている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2605_A7R01512_edit-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2605_A7R01512_edit-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>